{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_02_02",
  "title": "神崎莉央 2話 ゾンビでナース",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ハロウィンイベント当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The day of the Halloween event",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、{user}さん\n何よ、この衣装は！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ {user}-san!\nWhat on earth is this costume!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "資料に載っていたのと全然違うじゃない！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s completely different from the references you sent me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.633333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、デザイナーとイベント主催側の間で\n意思疎通がうまくいってなかったらしくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ looks like there was a miscommunication\nbetween the designer and the organizer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.033333333333335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ナースなのは分かってたけど\nこのコンセプトはなんなのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nurse I can understand.\nBut what on earth is this design concept?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "もっとコスプレ感は抑えめだったはずでしょ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wasn’t supposed to be so blatantly a cosplay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ゾンビでナースって……どんな世界観なのよ！\nこの子はどこで誰を看護してるの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who came up with the idea… of a zombie nurse?!\nWho’s she supposed to nurse?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.166666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "め、冥界で……亡者を相手にかな？\n……たぶん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Er… the dead‚ in‚ you know‚ the afterlife‚ I guess?\nMaybe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "こんな変な格好で、ステージに立ったら\nかえってマイナスイメージがつくわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What would it do to my image\nif I went on stage wearing this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "リーダーの私がこんな仕事をして\nLizNoirのファンが減ったらどうするのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What if LizNoir loses fans because the group’s leader\nis taking on jobs like this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、ポジティブに考えれば\n今までとは違うタイプのファンが増える可能性も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Think on the bright side.\nYou might gain different types of fans from this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "どんなタイプのファンなのよ！　じゃあ貴方は\nこの格好をした私のファンになれるの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What type of fan are you talking about?!\nWill you be a fan of someone who looks like THIS?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……\nど、努力すれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ummm…\nWell‚ with enough time and effort…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "努力しないと無理な時点で、ダメじゃない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then it’s no good at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……莉央さんの言う通りです。スタッフさんに話して\n違う仮装にしてもらうようにしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right… I’ll talk to the staff\nand see if we can get a different costume.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……やっぱり慣れない仕事を受けるのは――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh* I guess this is what I get for taking a job I’m not used to—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3866.6666666666742,
          "startTime": 79.73333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "メッセージだわ……誰かしら？\nえ？　愛とこころ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A text? Who is it from?\nEh? Ai and Kokoro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2766.6666666666656,
          "startTime": 84.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "『今日のイベント、こころと観に来てます\n莉央さんがどんな仮装をしてるのか楽しみです。愛』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Kokoro and I will be coming to watch today’s event.\nLooking forward to seeing Rio-san in costume. - Ai”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "『無難にカボチャの魔女とかだったらがっかりです！\n思い切り派手なの頼みますね。こころ』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“I would be so disappointed if it’s just your standard pumpkin and witch!\nI want to see something that really catches the eye! - Kokoro”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……ですって\nこの後輩達は、また私に余計なプレッシャーを……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what they wrote.\nMy terrible juniors are piling pressure on me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はは、愛とこころらしいですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ that’s so like Ai and Kokoro…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "…………もぉ～～～～っ！\n分かったわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Fine!\nI’ll do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、待って！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "…………衣装は変えないでいいわ\nゾンビのナース、OKよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…There’s no need to change the costume.\nI’ll do it. The zombie nurse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……いいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Are you sure?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
