      "bgName": "halloweenstage",
      "startTime": 158.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、こんばんは\nLizNoirの神崎莉央、です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good evening‚ everyone.\nI’m Rio Kanzaki‚ from LizNoir…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4966.666666666669,
          "startTime": 163.46666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage",
      "startTime": 165.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "……ううっ、視線を凄く感じるわ……\nそれも、今までとは全然違う視線を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hngh… I can feel everyone staring at me…\nAnd in completely different way than usual…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage",
      "startTime": 173.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみんなが戸惑っているのが\n手に取るように分かるわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can almost physically feel\nhow confused my fans are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "プレッシャーには慣れているつもりだったけど\nコスプレくらいで、こんなに緊張するなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought I was used to pressure…\nI can’t believe how cosplaying is making me so nervous…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage",
      "startTime": 184.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "でも、話さなきゃ……\nだけど、頭が真っ白に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to keep talking…\nBut I can’t think of anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage",
      "startTime": 190.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん！　俯いてちゃダメだ！\n顔を上げて！　ファンを見て下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san! Don’t look down!\nHold your head high! Look at the fans!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "どんな姿でも神崎莉央の魅力は消えたりしないです！\n君らしくやればいいんだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Be yourself! The charm of Rio Kanzaki never changes‚\nno matter what Rio-san wear!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage",
      "startTime": 201.76666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio027.m4a",
      "text": "私らしく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Be myself…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage",
      "startTime": 203.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio028.m4a",
      "text": "……そう、どんな格好をしても\n私は私だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s right. I’m myself‚\nno matter what I wear.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage",
      "startTime": 208.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio029.m4a",
      "text": "気高いLizNoirのリーダーとして\n恥ずかしくない仕事を――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As the proud leader of LizNoir‚\nI will put on a show that’s worthy of that name!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_halloweenstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "halloweenstage",
      "startTime": 213.56666666666666
    },
    {
